Summary: A 3D physics body that can't be moved by external forces but affects other bodies when moved manually.

AnimatableBody3D inherits from StaticBody3D < PhysicsBody3D < CollisionObject3D < Node3D < Node < Object

A 3D physics body that can't be moved by external forces. When moved manually, it affects other bodies in its path.
