Document: AnimatableBody3D
Path: godot/classes/class_animatablebody3d.rst
Summary: Property sync_to_physics and its behavior for physics synchronization

Property: sync_to_physics (bool) = true
Controls whether the body's movement is synchronized to the physics frame. Recommended for animation-based movement (e.g., AnimationPlayer). Key Rule: Do not use with PhysicsBody3D.move_and_collide().

Methods:
- set_sync_to_physics(value: bool)
- is_sync_to_physics_enabled() → bool

Note: Synchronization ensures smooth integration with physics simulations when using animated movement.